  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Math Teacher (Full - Time / Part - Time)",
  "description": "<h3><strong>Job Description</strong></h3><p>If you are looking to grow and make a real difference in your teaching career, we want you!</p><p>At <strong>Seriously Addictive Mathematics Jurong West</strong>, we believe in investing in our tutors’ professional growth. We are looking for passionate educators who are committed to the belief that every student can succeed, and that it is our mission to help them realize their fullest potential. </p><p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Conduct tailored lessons according to the centre’s customized learning plans for Primary Levels</p></li><li><p>Monitor and track the academic performance and progress of each student</p></li><li><p>Maintain clear communication with parents regarding student progress, providing constructive feedback and learning solutions</p></li><li><p>Review and contribute to the enhancement of lesson materials and centre programmes</p></li><li><p>Support general centre operations and other relevant duties as required</p></li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Diploma/Degree in relevant fields preferred</p></li><li><p>Passionate about teaching and student development</p></li><li><p>Open-minded, adaptable, and patient</p></li><li><p>Strong sense of responsibility and a positive “can-do” attitude</p></li><li><p>Excellent interpersonal and communication skills</p></li><li><p>Previous teaching or tutoring experience is advantageous</p></li></ul><p><strong>Working Hours :</strong></p><ul><li><p>Wed - Friday (1.30pm-9.30pm) & 2 weekends (9.30am-6.30pm)</p></li><li><p>Part-time arrangements are also available</p></li></ul><p><strong>Interested candidates, please submit your resume to jurongwest@seriouslyaddictivemaths.com.sg.</strong><br /><em>This position is open to Singapore Citizens and Permanent Residents only.</em></p>",
